  "translations": {
    "en": {
      "description": {
        "text": "A fine, varied crag on Värmdö, on the way to the Strömma area. High in places, but with good landings.",
        "method": "llm",
        "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
        "sourceIds": [
          "legacy:lynxklippan"
        ]
      },
      "sections": {
        "allmant": {
          "title": {
            "text": "General",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:lynxklippan"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "A fine, varied crag on Värmdö, on the way to the Strömma area. Some highballs, but with good landings.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:lynxklippan"
            ]
          }
        },
        "vagbeskrivning": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Directions",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:lynxklippan"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "title=Anneberg lat= 18484400 long=59298100\n\nBy car\n\nLocated by Lostigen in Skeppsdalsström (behind Värmdö Golf), clearly visible from the road. Park considerately.\n\nBy bus\n\nTake bus 433 or 434 from Slussen (about 25 minutes) and get off at Skeppdalström.\n\nFollow Svartträskvägen past Återvägen, Svartträsket and Dalgången. Turn right when you reach a T-junction with Lostigen. The crag is somewhere along Lostigen between numbers 33 and 72.\n\nIt is about a 15-minute walk from the bus stop.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:lynxklippan"
            ]
          }
        },
        "sektor-1": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Sector 1",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:lynxklippan"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "The crag sections are presented in order from the road into the woods.\n\nThe first crag from the road.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:lynxklippan"
            ]
          }
        },
        "sektor-2": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Sector 2",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
